# Build contexts should not include caches, build outputs, or vendored deps.
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.github
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/.DS_Store

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/*.tsbuildinfo

api/.gradle
api/build
api/bin
api/out

# Test coverage report dirs only — anchored so they don't swallow the
# app.beat.coverage Java package or web/render coverage source dirs.
/coverage/
**/web/coverage/
**/render/coverage/
api/build/reports/

**/*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
